author: Zack Meisel, cleveland.com
title: Jinx? Anti-jinx? Sports Illustrated projects Los Angeles Dodgers over Cleveland Indians in 2017 World Series
text: SI has tabbed the Los Angeles Dodgers as its selection for 2017 World Series champion and the outlet foresees the Indians as the Fall Classic runner-ups for the second consecutive season.
